        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Characterized by the inescapable cold—and subsequent shivering—that slowly pervades the victim’s body, barnacle shivers is a disease that infects creatures attacked by blood barnacles. Until the disease is cured, the infected creature can’t regain hp except by magical means, and its hp maximum decreases by 3 (1d6) for every 24 hours that elapse. This reduction lasts until the disease is cured. The creature dies if the disease reduces its hp maximum to 0. A Humanoid or Beast slain by this disease rises 24 hours later as a zombie. The zombie isn’t under the blood barnacle’s control, but it views the blood barnacle as an ally.",
